description=Autonomous AI agent-as-OS for Android. Installs peko-agent + peko-llm-daemon into /system/bin with boot-time services, multi-provider cloud chain (Anthropic/OpenRouter/OpenAI/Groq/...), full autonomy stack, and optional floating overlay app. Web UI on :8080. Tested on OnePlus 6T (fajita) / arm64.
